    CAP. CXCIX.---De sene quodam simplice, qui, cum sacramentum [Col. CXLVIII] offerret, angelos videbat Ibid.
    CAP. CC.---Quomodo juvenis aurifex a viro patricio sit in filium adoptatus. 229
